        "created_at": "2018-03-01T22:24:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=1770978\"><strong>2012 Hubert Lamy Puligny-Montrachet Les Tremblots Cuv\u00e9e Haute Densit\u00e9</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Puligny-Montrachet (3/1/2018)</em><br>\nSuper compact and tight. There\u2019s plenty of struck match to the aroma. It has pristine lemon, green melon and white peach fruits. It is sharp, linear and intense with loads of chalky dry extract on the back-end. Great wine.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
